WEBVTT

00:01.142 --> 00:03.652
- From now on, I'll stay out of your life.
- Maybe that's for the best.

00:03.682 --> 00:05.683
I think you picked that fight
because you were jealous.

00:05.713 --> 00:07.740
Of Theo? Don't be ridiculous!

00:08.484 --> 00:10.211
Do I smell a show-mance?

00:10.538 --> 00:12.301
This morning, we had one
secret between us.

00:12.331 --> 00:14.123
- Now we have two.
- I know this will probably

00:14.125 --> 00:15.708
make everybody hate me,

00:15.738 --> 00:18.377
but I'm not really a lesbian.

00:20.630 --> 00:22.484
Have a great rest
of your day, Hesterians.

00:22.514 --> 00:24.005
And remember to take the High Road

00:24.035 --> 00:25.943
and give your best
wishes to Karma Ashcroft,

00:25.973 --> 00:27.859
'cause even someone that fakes lesbianism

00:27.889 --> 00:30.388
and offends an entire persecuted minority

00:30.418 --> 00:32.231
deserves a happy 16th birthday.

00:32.470 --> 00:33.826
♪ Am I the only one
that feels emotion ♪

00:33.828 --> 00:35.937
- (Cell phone vibrates)
- (Coughs)

00:36.106 --> 00:38.239
Hey there, my B-Day BFF.

00:38.509 --> 00:41.017
How sweet has 16 been?
Toothache inducing?

00:41.047 --> 00:43.221
Less sweet, more bitter,

00:43.251 --> 00:44.889
especially with you home sick.

00:44.919 --> 00:46.228
Maybe it's karma.

00:46.582 --> 00:49.595
Not... me, Karma. I mean "karma" Karma.

00:49.625 --> 00:51.203
I'm not following.

00:51.233 --> 00:52.100
(Sighs)

00:52.130 --> 00:53.698
I admitted to being a fake lesbian,

00:53.728 --> 00:55.073
and now I'm a pariah.

00:55.275 --> 00:57.848
Maybe the fates have also
placed a pox on your house.

00:57.878 --> 01:00.257
Okay, cliff-notes, it's not a pox.

01:00.287 --> 01:01.576
It's strep.

01:01.606 --> 01:02.967
And the only karma I believe in

01:02.997 --> 01:05.358
is the one who can eat
her weight in cake frosting.

01:05.388 --> 01:08.144
♪ I couldn't see anything ♪

01:09.314 --> 01:12.248
- ♪ But I still feel the same ♪
- It just sucks not to be celebrating

01:12.278 --> 01:14.360
with the people I care about most.

01:14.546 --> 01:17.004
- People?
- Person. Singular.

01:17.034 --> 01:21.065
(Laughs) As in you, my
strep-stricken soul sister.

01:21.095 --> 01:24.744
Well, I promise I won't miss
any more milestone birthdays.

01:25.885 --> 01:27.914
For your 18th, we'll buy porn.

01:27.944 --> 01:29.862
And there's 21... that one's obvious.

01:30.166 --> 01:32.919
And for your 50th, Alaskan cruise.

01:32.921 --> 01:35.613
I'm thinking we'll be pretty
into whale watching by then.

01:35.643 --> 01:36.843
Where'd you go? Karma?

01:36.873 --> 01:39.481
I'm here. I just got to my locker.

01:39.981 --> 01:41.883
♪ So go your own way ♪

01:41.913 --> 01:44.047
♪ I believe too ♪

01:44.049 --> 01:45.181
♪ Just think of me ♪

01:45.183 --> 01:47.462
♪ Ba-by right here tonight ♪

01:47.492 --> 01:48.901
Surprise!

01:49.137 --> 01:51.521
Amy! What are you doing here?

01:51.523 --> 01:54.779
I faked sick to set up your greatest
birthday scavenger hunt to date.

01:55.692 --> 01:57.198
What's up with the longing Liam looks?

01:57.228 --> 01:58.383
I thought you two were through.

01:58.413 --> 02:01.212
Oh, we are. Completely dunzo.

02:01.432 --> 02:04.151
- Trust me.
- (Laughs nervously)

02:04.842 --> 02:06.546
- Are you sure?
- Totally.

02:06.576 --> 02:08.205
And you didn't have to go
through all this trouble.

02:08.235 --> 02:09.872
I mean, after the week
that I've been having,

02:09.902 --> 02:11.521
I don't really feel like celebrating.

02:11.551 --> 02:13.502
You're a social leper, so what?

02:13.532 --> 02:16.007
Soon we'll go back to being
ignored like the good old days.

02:16.037 --> 02:17.155
All we need is each other.

02:17.185 --> 02:19.308
And to prove that point,

02:19.611 --> 02:22.195
I have recreated key
moments in our friendship.

02:22.225 --> 02:25.955
That's right... this hunt is
the best of Karmy retrospective.

02:25.985 --> 02:27.957
Has anyone ever told you
you're the best friend ever?

02:27.987 --> 02:29.435
Yeah.

02:29.739 --> 02:31.418
Let's do this.

02:33.674 --> 02:34.516
Uh...

02:34.546 --> 02:36.057
Today is your day.

02:36.087 --> 02:38.310
I'm not gonna let you carry your book-bag

02:38.340 --> 02:39.890
like some sort of commoner.

02:40.750 --> 02:44.273
Now here, open your first clue.

02:45.605 --> 02:48.327
Yay, I... can't wait to read it.

02:48.357 --> 02:49.625
(Upbeat electronic music)

02:49.655 --> 02:53.367
- sync & corrections by wolfen -
- www.addic7ed.com -

02:54.462 --> 02:55.322
Liam.

02:55.352 --> 02:57.587
Quit taking it out on these
innocent art supplies...

02:57.589 --> 02:59.388
Shane, really, I don't
want to talk about it.

02:59.418 --> 03:01.543
That's just your straight guy resistance

03:01.573 --> 03:03.398
to talking about your feelings.

03:03.428 --> 03:04.379
Push through it.

03:04.409 --> 03:05.889
- What are y'all on about?
- (Sighs)

03:05.919 --> 03:08.714
It's Karma's birthday, and Liam
can't be with her for reasons

03:08.744 --> 03:11.856
too complicated and
(bleep) up to specify.

03:11.886 --> 03:14.075
Wanna go hit stuff?
Always makes me feel better.

03:14.105 --> 03:15.688
I'm taking this mixed martial
arts class downtown.

03:15.690 --> 03:19.170
Nice try, Theo, but what Liam
needs is to talk it all out

03:19.200 --> 03:21.546
over some grilled
cheeses at Millie's Diner.

03:21.576 --> 03:22.815
What is this,<i> The View?</i>

03:22.845 --> 03:25.114
(Both laughing)

03:26.108 --> 03:29.141
Shane, I'm sorry, but that class
is just what the doctor ordered.

03:29.171 --> 03:31.414
You're not the doctor.
You're the patient.

03:31.444 --> 03:32.899
