04:17.502 --> 04:19.605
- That is ridiculous.
- Is it?

04:19.635 --> 04:21.226
Is it, really?

04:22.119 --> 04:24.489
Fine, maybe I was thinking
we might bump...

04:24.519 --> 04:27.125
- Uglies?
- Into each other.

04:27.155 --> 04:28.354
I like him, okay?

04:28.384 --> 04:30.051
So you better not screw it up.

04:30.081 --> 04:33.397
Trust me, I won't. I am all
for you two mating.

04:33.427 --> 04:34.822
- You are?
- A high-maintenance,

04:34.852 --> 04:37.986
time-consuming girlfriend
is exactly what Theo needs.

04:37.988 --> 04:39.321
Right? Okay.

04:39.323 --> 04:41.594
So how can we make this happen?

04:43.694 --> 04:45.527
Amy, this is amazing!

04:45.529 --> 04:47.689
It's just like that ball pit where
we met in kindergarten.

04:47.719 --> 04:48.801
And you know what?

04:48.831 --> 04:50.824
I don't even care that my room's
gonna reek of toddler feet

04:50.854 --> 04:52.307
- for the next month.
- You better get to searching.

04:52.337 --> 04:54.119
- We don't have all day.
- Right.

04:54.121 --> 04:55.516
- Wait... what?
- Your next clue's

04:55.546 --> 04:58.957
written on one of these
balls, so start digging!

04:58.959 --> 05:00.824
- Really?
- Uh-huh.

05:01.246 --> 05:03.045
Uh...Fun! Ha.

05:03.299 --> 05:04.596
Here goes.

05:07.930 --> 05:10.525
I may have underestimated
how long this would take.

05:10.555 --> 05:12.581
I'll help.

05:19.901 --> 05:20.862
Hey!

05:22.579 --> 05:23.405
What's that?

05:23.435 --> 05:26.151
Uh, just a... birthday note

05:26.153 --> 05:28.153
from Irma.

05:30.086 --> 05:32.386
- Irma the lunch lady?
- What can I say?

05:32.416 --> 05:34.209
She is a fan.

05:34.211 --> 05:35.577
On my birthday, she just gave me

05:35.579 --> 05:37.379
an extra scoop of mashed potatoes.

05:37.381 --> 05:38.921
But you know the rules....

05:38.951 --> 05:41.466
We open gifts and cards after cake time.

05:41.468 --> 05:43.001
- Of course!
- Now, come on.

05:43.003 --> 05:45.453
This clue ball ain't gonna find itself.

05:50.427 --> 05:51.678
(Guys grunting)

05:51.708 --> 05:53.965
So when does the punching
of things commence?

05:53.995 --> 05:56.765
Patience, young Padawan.
First there's warm-ups.

05:56.767 --> 06:00.407
Great! We're so ready to bust
some skulls and whatnot.

06:00.437 --> 06:02.262
Well, well, well. Look who it is.

06:02.292 --> 06:04.323
You two came together? Are you...

06:04.325 --> 06:05.607
- Friends now?
- What?

06:05.609 --> 06:06.897
- Eew! No.
- Don't be gross.

06:06.927 --> 06:09.075
I just ran into Lauren here,
and it just so happens

06:09.105 --> 06:11.263
she's in the mood to whack
on someone herself

06:11.265 --> 06:12.681
or was it whack off, Lauren?

06:12.683 --> 06:13.932
Whack on, whack off, whack on...

06:13.934 --> 06:15.416
- I'm looking to...
- Ow!

06:15.446 --> 06:17.019
Mix up my workout regime.

06:17.021 --> 06:18.953
Yoga-lates is getting old.

06:18.983 --> 06:21.974
I'm gonna go... stretch.

06:21.976 --> 06:24.189
(Gasps) I saw that!

06:24.219 --> 06:26.445
You've got a thing for the ice queen!

06:26.447 --> 06:28.121
You two would be so cute together.

06:28.151 --> 06:30.582
Plus, if he melts her heart,
you'll save all the villagers!

06:30.612 --> 06:32.503
There you go thinking you're right again.

06:32.533 --> 06:35.610
- Seriously, butt out.
- And butt joke in three,

06:35.640 --> 06:37.289
- two, and one.
- Please!

06:37.291 --> 06:38.746
Butt jokes are beneath me.

06:38.776 --> 06:40.359
But speaking of butts...

06:40.361 --> 06:43.012
- (Guys grunting)
- I was so wrong about one thing.

06:43.042 --> 06:44.491
This class isn't too straight.

06:44.521 --> 06:46.662
This is the gayest thing I have ever seen!

06:46.692 --> 06:49.009
- What? No it isn't!
- Uh... Come on!

06:49.039 --> 06:51.827
Half-naked, sweaty men,
colorful short-shorts,

06:51.857 --> 06:54.118
positions straight out
of a Sean Cody film.

06:54.148 --> 06:55.500
You're crazy! Back me up, Liam.

06:55.530 --> 06:57.639
You are talking to the undisputed expert

06:57.669 --> 06:59.843
of finding homoerotic subtext in anything.

06:59.873 --> 07:01.597
Do not get him started on Batman.

07:01.599 --> 07:04.184
