cave and design outfits.

07:04.214 --> 07:07.491
Okay, I'll give you that one.
But MMA is not gay... in any way.

07:07.521 --> 07:09.614
- Ooh!
- Take it!

07:09.644 --> 07:11.440
All right, huddle up, class.

07:11.442 --> 07:13.976
I'm your instructor, Duke Lewis Junior.

07:13.978 --> 07:15.394
My father owns this gym.

07:15.396 --> 07:17.329
Kinda like how I'm about to own...

07:17.359 --> 07:18.906
All your asses.

07:18.936 --> 07:20.680
- Who's ready?
- (Claps)

07:22.987 --> 07:24.360
Wow, you really went all out.

07:24.390 --> 07:27.044
I mean, painting ceramic
figurines from our unicorn period

07:27.074 --> 07:29.202
and then sneaking into that PG-13 movie?

07:29.232 --> 07:31.326
That was so us when we were ten.

07:31.328 --> 07:33.314
But did we really have
to stay for the whole thing?

07:33.753 --> 07:36.331
We're not cutting corners
on your birthday!

07:39.643 --> 07:41.509
- Surprise.
- Surprise!

07:41.539 --> 07:42.356
Mom...

07:42.386 --> 07:44.615
- And Aunt Sarah.
- You know my sister

07:44.645 --> 07:46.625
prefers her chosen name:

07:46.627 --> 07:50.101
Your psychic Aunt Sage has come
all the way from Sedona

07:50.131 --> 07:53.354
- to read your tea leaves.
- Wow. Just like when we were 13.

07:53.384 --> 07:56.812
Mm-hmm. Gather forth, spirit sisters.

07:56.842 --> 07:58.713
A divination is just what you need.

07:58.743 --> 08:01.106
That, and one of my
♪ magic brownies! ♪

08:01.108 --> 08:02.558
(Gasps) Ooh!

08:02.862 --> 08:04.448
Oh, wait. (Sniffs)

08:04.650 --> 08:07.279
Just making sure they're not
your father's magic brownies.

08:07.281 --> 08:09.346
- Mm!
- So after tea drinkin'

08:09.376 --> 08:12.405
and fortune tellin', is it time
for cake eatin' and card openin'?

08:12.435 --> 08:13.804
Hey, no spoilers.

08:13.834 --> 08:16.405
Just relax and live in the now.

08:16.407 --> 08:18.369
- (Mouthing words)
- Right.

08:24.185 --> 08:25.380
Oh, that's hot!

08:25.382 --> 08:26.832
Interesting.

08:26.834 --> 08:30.558
It appears the universe has
a very important message for you

08:30.588 --> 08:33.337
about your one true love.

08:35.739 --> 08:37.913
Well, tell the universe I can't
wait to find out what it says.

08:37.943 --> 08:39.178
(Gasps) Not so fast.

08:39.179 --> 08:42.212
A force is trying to keep
the message from you,

08:42.241 --> 08:45.400
standing between you and your love.

08:45.841 --> 08:48.347
Well, what could it be? They're
sitting right next to other.

08:48.377 --> 08:50.291
Whatever it is, act now

08:50.321 --> 08:51.960
before it's too late.

08:53.444 --> 08:56.467
Wow! Well, that tea really
shot right through me.

08:57.104 --> 08:59.364
I have to visit the little
birthday girl's room.

08:59.366 --> 09:00.833
Excuse me.

09:01.325 --> 09:03.669
Mind if I borrow this?
It's a little drafty in there.

09:03.671 --> 09:05.021
Okay.

09:09.427 --> 09:11.971
- (Bleep)!
- Honey, whatcha looking for?

09:12.001 --> 09:13.462
I can't find that note.

09:13.464 --> 09:15.848
- Oh, who's it from?
- Irma.

09:15.850 --> 09:18.565
- Irma the lunch lady?
- Apparently, she's a fan.

09:18.595 --> 09:20.436
- Aw!
- It must have slipped out!

09:20.466 --> 09:21.386
Where could it be?

09:21.388 --> 09:23.155
(Sighs) No telling.

09:23.661 --> 09:27.068
But I doubt Irma wrote much
more than "happy birthday."

09:27.456 --> 09:29.413
She has a poet's soul.

09:29.884 --> 09:33.065
Come on, we have to retrace
our steps until we find it.

09:34.922 --> 09:36.118
Bye.

09:36.920 --> 09:38.558
This isn't making me feel any better.

09:38.588 --> 09:39.838
That's because I'm right.

09:39.840 --> 09:41.289
Those grilled cheeses are calling us.

09:41.291 --> 09:43.188
Or we need to skip this lame warm up

09:43.218 --> 09:45.042
and get to the part where we
get to whale on something.

09:45.072 --> 09:47.545
Remember, keep those abs tight.

09:48.141 --> 09:49.714
Those abs!

09:50.163 --> 09:51.571
- I knew it!
- Knew what?

09:51.601 --> 09:52.612
Switch!

09:56.135 --> 09:57.208
Still think this is gay?

09:57.238 --> 10:00.355
Oh, this gay-ole-time
just got even gayer.

10:00.385 --> 10:03.776
Our instructor is queerer than
Neil Patrick Harris at the tonys.

10:03.806 --> 10:06.144
Duke Lewis is the best
junior division MMA fighter

10:06.174 --> 10:07.899
in the state... He could
go pro any minute.

10:07.901 --> 10:10.198
- And he couldn't also be gay?
- He also has a rep

10:10.228 --> 10:12.941
as a total hound dog. One
that chases the pussy-cat,

10:12.971 --> 10:14.420
not the rooster.

10:14.656 --> 10:16.203
Care to make things interesting?

10:16.233 --> 10:17.705
50 bucks interesting enough?

10:17.735 --> 10:21.072
Done. Oh, and P.S., I've seen
Duke's abs all over stubble.

10:21.392 --> 10:22.737
The gay hook-up app!

10:22.767 --> 10:25.224
