memory for torsos!

10:25.254 --> 10:26.467
Switch!

10:30.898 --> 10:32.848
All right. Nice toss.

10:32.878 --> 10:34.696
There's more to you than meets the eye.

10:34.726 --> 10:35.971
What's that supposed to mean?

10:36.001 --> 10:38.752
You're so dainty and
fragile and feminine.

10:38.782 --> 10:40.337
But really, you... ooh!

10:40.367 --> 10:41.896
I'm what?

10:41.926 --> 10:44.451
Okay! Warm-ups are over.

10:44.453 --> 10:47.008
Now I need a brave volunteer
to help demonstrate

10:47.038 --> 10:48.926
some basic fighting holds with me.

10:48.956 --> 10:50.467
Any takers?

10:51.584 --> 10:53.627
See what you got, pretty boy.

10:55.889 --> 10:57.423
We're never gonna find it, Karma.

10:57.453 --> 10:58.518
Let's get back to the hunt.

10:58.548 --> 11:00.878
We only got three stops
left until cake time.

11:00.908 --> 11:02.125
Five more minutes!

11:02.155 --> 11:04.671
Had to be in the ball pit, of all places.

11:04.994 --> 11:07.118
I can't believe I didn't
think of this earlier.

11:07.148 --> 11:10.202
Why don't we just call Irma
and ask her what it said?

11:10.762 --> 11:12.179
Wait. You have Irma's number?

11:12.181 --> 11:13.577
Of course. Up until a few months ago,

11:13.607 --> 11:16.038
she was our only friend, remember?

11:16.421 --> 11:19.134
Maybe she'll finally give me
that oatmeal cookie recipe.

11:19.164 --> 11:20.685
Wait, wait...

11:20.988 --> 11:23.162
It's not from Irma.

11:23.640 --> 11:25.831
- It's from Liam.
- Finally.

11:25.861 --> 11:27.632
- The truth comes out.
- You knew?

11:27.662 --> 11:29.182
I've known this whole time.

11:29.212 --> 11:31.289
I saw you two having
eye sex in the courtyard.

11:31.319 --> 11:34.262
I've barely seen him. I don't
even know what it says.

11:34.292 --> 11:37.287
Here. Now you can find out.

11:38.320 --> 11:40.157
You've had it? I can't believe

11:40.159 --> 11:43.093
