- Well, now you know how it feels.

11:43.123 --> 11:44.458
Today was supposed to be about us,

11:44.488 --> 11:45.718
but here he is, Liam Booker,

11:45.748 --> 11:47.235
just when I thought
we moved past all that.

11:47.265 --> 11:48.604
Are you serious?

11:48.634 --> 11:51.205
We just spent four hours
reliving our past.

11:51.235 --> 11:53.372
You two are banging behind
my back again, aren't you?

11:53.402 --> 11:54.788
What? No, we're not.

11:54.818 --> 11:56.155
