11:56.185 --> 11:58.970
I swear, there's nothing
going on between us.

11:59.000 --> 12:01.577
- I chose you.
- Chose me?

12:01.607 --> 12:02.723
What the hell are you talking about?

12:02.753 --> 12:06.299
I knew I couldn't be with Liam and
keep our friendship, so I chose you!

12:06.329 --> 12:08.395
Well, it doesn't feel that way.

12:09.004 --> 12:12.523
What more do I have to do
to prove it to you, Amy?

12:17.037 --> 12:19.632
There. Are you happy?

12:27.905 --> 12:31.565
Oh! I didn't expect you
to be back so soon.

12:31.595 --> 12:32.862
You and Karma don't usually finish

12:32.892 --> 12:34.916
her birthday scavenger
hunt until midnight.

12:34.946 --> 12:37.169
- We had a really bad fight.
- Was this a...

12:37.199 --> 12:39.437
Friend fight or a...

12:39.467 --> 12:41.704
More than friends fight?
I'm still not really clear

12:41.734 --> 12:44.450
- on the whole...
- Mom, Karma loves guys.

12:44.480 --> 12:45.420
And you?

12:45.450 --> 12:49.254
I love Karma. That's the whole problem.

